2001-11-04	Bertrand Demiddelaer <bert@zehc.net>

	* release 4.5

	* don't abort anymore on corrupted log lines

	* set BUFFER_SIZE value to 32Ko
	
	
2001-21-03	Bertrand Demiddelaer <bert@zehc.net>

	* release 4.4

	* fixed a major bug on a broken month initialization
	
	
2001-05-03	Bertrand Demiddelaer <bert@zehc.net>

	* release 4.3

	* corrections on manpages

	* fix in configure.in to abort if zlib is not present

	* fixed a potential segmentation fault on malformed log lines
	

2001-22-01	Bertrand Demiddelaer <bert@zehc.net>

	* release 4.2

	* autoconf compliant thanks to Igor Genibel <igor@genibel.org>


2001-07-01	Bertrand Demiddelaer <bert@zehc.net>

	* release 4.1

	* fixed a new bug for empty log files
	
	* optimizations of the new system of date comparison

	* set BUFFER_SIZE value to 16Ko instead of 8Ko

	* some clean up in the critical loop

	* fixed and updated code comments


2001-05-01	Bertrand Demiddelaer <bert@zehc.net>

	* release 4.0

	* massive code clean up

	* fixed the lock problem due to date jump back in log files

	* minor fixes and optimizations


