	* release 3.3

	* optimizations on 'fast_gzgets'

	* added a support for empty log files 

	* minor optimizations


2001-02-01	Bertrand Demiddelaer <bert@zehc.net>

	* release 3.2

	* minor optimizations

	* use of 'write' instead of 'fputs' in the critical loop


2000-29-12	Bertrand Demiddelaer <bert@zehc.net>

	* release 3.1

	* fixed a potential bug with too many gzipped files in argument

	* implementation of a faster replacement for 'memcmp' in the critical loop


2000-28-12	Bertrand Demiddelaer <bert@zehc.net>

	* release 3.0

	* added some code to replace gzgets by a faster gzip support 


2000-02-11	Bertrand Demiddelaer <bert@zehc.net>

	* release 2.1

	* implementation of a faster replacement for 'localtime'

